data.description: BACK ON MARKET- NO FAULT OF SELLER. Rare opportunity to a own a stunning, nearly brand new home in the heart of Midtown. This 2-story gem is situated in one of the city's most rapidly evolving neighborhoods, where innovation & growth are ever-present. Completed in Dec 2022, this luxurious property boasts premium finishes throughout, emanating an air of elegance & style. Step inside & be greeted by gorgeous laminate flooring, an inviting living room, warm dining area, & conveniently located half bathroom. The kitchen is a true highlight, boasting exquisite quartz countertops & sleek stainless-steel appliances, enhancing both aesthetics & functionality. Walk upstairs to find 3 beds, 2 baths, & a spacious 2nd-floor balcony. This property offers a rear driveway & large privacy fenced yard, creating the perfect space for your enjoyment & relaxation. With its prime location, you are only a 5-min drive to Downtown Savannah, 15-min drive to Tybee Island, & a short walk to Daffin Park!
